Class DrillByteArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.expr.fn.impl.DrillByteArray

  • public class DrillByteArray
extends Object
    Thin wrapper around byte array. This class is used by aggregate functions which consume decimal, variable width vectors as inputs.
